HEADWORD: Polypharmacy
<hw>Pol`y*phar"ma*cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Poly-</ets> + Gr. <?/ the using of medicine, fr. <?/
